## File Patterns

### Python Files
```python
"""Module docstring with basic description."""

import logging
from typing import Dict, Any

logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)

class ClassName:
    """Class docstring with basic description."""

    def method_name(self, param: Dict[str, Any]) -> bool:
        """Method docstring with basic description."""
        try:
            result = self._process(param)
            return result
        except Exception as e:
            logger.error("Error in method_name: %s", str(e))
            raise
```

### Configuration Files
```yaml
# Basic configuration structure
type: "test"
name: "test-name"
url: "https://example.com"
frequency: 300
nodes:
  - "US-East"
  - "US-West"
```

## Globs
- "**/*.py"              # Python source files
- "**/*.yaml"           # YAML configuration files
- "**/*.md"            # Documentation files
